# ============================================
# VERCEL PRODUCTION ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ============================================
# COPY THESE VALUES INTO VERCEL DASHBOARD
# Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# ============================================

# REQUIRED: MongoDB Atlas Connection
# Get from: https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
# Format: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/dbname?retryWrites=true&w=majority
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://ai_mentor_user:YOUR_PASSWORD_HERE@cluster0.xyz.mongodb.net/ai-money-mentor?retryWrites=true&w=majority
MONGODB_DB=ai-money-mentor

# OPTIONAL: OpenAI API Key
# Get from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# OPTIONAL: Google Gemini API Key
# Get from: https://ai.google.dev/
# GOOGLE_GEMINI_API_KEY=...
# GOOGLE_GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-pro

# OPTIONAL: OpenRouter API Key
# Get from: https://openrouter.ai/
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
# OPENROUTER_MODEL=openrouter-model-name

# ============================================
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# ============================================
# 1. Get MongoDB Atlas connection string (see VERCEL_DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md)
# 2. Go to Vercel Dashboard
# 3. Click your project (ai-money-mentor)
# 4. Settings → Environment Variables
# 5. Add MONGODB_URI and MONGODB_DB
# 6. (Optional) Add API keys if you have them
# 7. Redeploy the project
# ============================================
